T*
(- Explain the meaning of Non-metals in Chemistry using accurate subject vocabulary.) Tj
T*
(- Describe the key ideas behind contrasting non-metal properties and common examples.) Tj
T*
(- Apply Non-metals to examples such as explaining why sulfur and oxygen behave) Tj
T*
(differently from metals.) Tj
