(Step-By-Step Method) Tj
T*
(1. Read the question or example and identify the part connected to Non-metals.) Tj
T*
(2. Recall the specific rule, process, or principle behind contrasting non-metal) Tj
T*
(properties and common examples.) Tj
T*
(3. Apply the correct chemical reasoning process step by step instead of jumping to the) Tj
T*
(answer.) Tj
T*
(4. Check the result carefully and confirm that it matches the requirement of the topic.) Tj
