T*
(Worked Example 1) Tj
T*
(1. Start with an example based on explaining why sulfur and oxygen behave differently) Tj
T*
(from metals.) Tj
T*
(2. Identify the exact idea in contrasting non-metal properties and common examples that) Tj
T*
(the question is testing.) Tj
